name: $200 Gift Certificate
description:
Know that person that's been talking about learning woodworking for years?
Or a hobbyist who might like access to a factory full of professional
equipment? Or maybe you think mom just might make a badass welder.

ADX membership, classes, and services such as custom laser engraving make
great gifts for anyone - from professional makers through those who've
never touched a table saw. Pick one up online, or at our front desk!

Gift Certificates will be mailed to you, and may be redeemed in person at the shop.
